'''Hungary''' is an original [[Nations|country]] that was added to BitLife in version 1.36. Its default cities are the capital, Budapest, along with Debrecen.

Alongside with [[Vietnam]] and [[South Korea]], the bitizen's last name go first (eg. Horthy Miklos) (last, first)

